  "detailed_description": "<h1>Steam Workshop</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Online Multiplayer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play Disc Golf with people all around the world! Challenge your friends, play a round with strangers. Play for fun or strive to become the best player in Disc Golf Online. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/dfec3cf7a2104bd21c8d99d01c210e55.poster.avif?t=1747081132\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/dfec3cf7a2104bd21c8d99d01c210e55.webm?t=1747081132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/dfec3cf7a2104bd21c8d99d01c210e55.mp4?t=1747081132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Community Made Maps</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own Disc Golf courses, and play them Online with your friends! Build the perfect course and upload it for other players to enjoy. Disc Golf Online has steam workshop integration, which makes it easy to browse, download and play community maps. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/cc9a9bf06305570dc6267cc7fd8654ae.poster.avif?t=1747081132\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/cc9a9bf06305570dc6267cc7fd8654ae.webm?t=1747081132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/cc9a9bf06305570dc6267cc7fd8654ae.mp4?t=1747081132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Procedural Generation</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Never run out of courses to play! A smart algorithm creates new course layouts and builds interesting terrain around it. Just enter a seed and the algorithm will produce a unique course from it. You can always save your favourite courses to play them again later. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/33b0305d8cca9b68644e640a98c242df.poster.avif?t=1747081132\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/33b0305d8cca9b68644e640a98c242df.webm?t=1747081132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/33b0305d8cca9b68644e640a98c242df.mp4?t=1747081132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Physics Simulation</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A flying disc is no easy physics problem, and a lot of simulations get it wrong. Disc Golf Online uses an aerodynamics-based approach that tries to mimic how the disc interacts with air around it. The physics model is carefully calibrated with real disc flights, to ensure the most realistic disc physics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/229b0b06c9faf6d8354233215acfb69a.poster.avif?t=1747081132\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/229b0b06c9faf6d8354233215acfb69a.webm?t=1747081132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/229b0b06c9faf6d8354233215acfb69a.mp4?t=1747081132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Online Multiplayer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play Disc Golf with people all around the world! Challenge your friends, play a round with strangers. Play for fun or strive to become the best player in Disc Golf Online. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/dfec3cf7a2104bd21c8d99d01c210e55.poster.avif?t=1747081132\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/dfec3cf7a2104bd21c8d99d01c210e55.webm?t=1747081132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/dfec3cf7a2104bd21c8d99d01c210e55.mp4?t=1747081132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Community Made Maps</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own Disc Golf courses, and play them Online with your friends! Build the perfect course and upload it for other players to enjoy. Disc Golf Online has steam workshop integration, which makes it easy to browse, download and play community maps. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/cc9a9bf06305570dc6267cc7fd8654ae.poster.avif?t=1747081132\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/cc9a9bf06305570dc6267cc7fd8654ae.webm?t=1747081132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/cc9a9bf06305570dc6267cc7fd8654ae.mp4?t=1747081132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Procedural Generation</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Never run out of courses to play! A smart algorithm creates new course layouts and builds interesting terrain around it. Just enter a seed and the algorithm will produce a unique course from it. You can always save your favourite courses to play them again later. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/33b0305d8cca9b68644e640a98c242df.poster.avif?t=1747081132\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/33b0305d8cca9b68644e640a98c242df.webm?t=1747081132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/33b0305d8cca9b68644e640a98c242df.mp4?t=1747081132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Physics Simulation</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A flying disc is no easy physics problem, and a lot of simulations get it wrong. Disc Golf Online uses an aerodynamics-based approach that tries to mimic how the disc interacts with air around it. The physics model is carefully calibrated with real disc flights, to ensure the most realistic disc physics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/229b0b06c9faf6d8354233215acfb69a.poster.avif?t=1747081132\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/229b0b06c9faf6d8354233215acfb69a.webm?t=1747081132\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2083540/extras/229b0b06c9faf6d8354233215acfb69a.mp4?t=1747081132\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
